<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1788576-i-want-to-read-the-cotton-malone-series">I want to read the Cotton Malone series, but really don&#39;t want to read another &quot;Christianity is wrong&quot; book....do I need to read the first one? Will I miss out on too much if I start with the second one?</a>
</div>
