        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1098090178" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18336101177723845995">So fascinated by the amount of research that went into this. Really cool book, and I&apos;m excited to follow Cotton on more adventures!</span>
  <span id="freeText18336101177723845995" style="display:none">So fascinated by the amount of research that went into this. Really cool book, and I'm excited to follow Cotton on more adventures!</span>
  <a data-text-id="18336101177723845995" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


