<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer7780156778752956413"> <br/><br/>Steve Berry is the <em>New York Times</em> and #1 internationally bestselling author of nineteen novels, which include: <a href='https://steveberry.org/books/the-warsaw-protocol/synopsis/' rel='nofollow noopener'>
