  <span id="freeText7780156778752956413" style="display:none"> <br /><br />Steve Berry is the <em>New York Times</em> and #1 internationally bestselling author of nineteen novels, which include: <a href="https://steveberry.org/books/the-warsaw-protocol/synopsis/" rel="nofollow noopener">
